Trick or Treat! 🎃 RNBW & PLUGPLAY are bringing you another exclusive opportunity at Escape ‘24 to trick or treat with one of our favorite artists, @imomnom 🙌

Stop by our booth this Friday from 8:00 to 8:30 PM for a chance to meet OMNOM and snag a goodie bag filled with his favorite Halloween munchies! 🍬 It’s first-come, first-served—so make sure to arrive early!
